The A. Philip Randolph Collection consists of the following series:

                Family Papers, 1942-1963;

                General Correspondence, 1925-1978;

                Subject Files, 1909-1978;

                Speeches and writings File, 1941-1978;

                Biographical File, 1945-1979; and,

                Miscellany, 1920-1979.
